TUBERCULOSIS, BOVINE, WILDLIFE - SOUTH AFRICA (03)
**************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
<http://www.fas.org/promed/ahead>
[The survey announced in the previous posting has, apparently, started. The
following edited account appeared on AP, 21 October. - Mod.MHJ]
